{"tid":1162723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[小鳳姐有請] Google將暫停與華為合作","createTime":"2019-05-20T04:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:43:45.000Z","uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"154829d135c2fb57a33c5213c4eadf9d03ffd972","tid":1162723,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"美國商務部上周將中國電訊商華為列入貿易黑名單後，據路透社引述消息報道，Google已打算暫停與華為的部分商業合作，華為除了仍可使用開放原始碼的軟件及相關產品外，Google已暫停向華為提供涉及Android作業系統的技術支援。<br />\n<br />\n若消息屬實，在中國以外地區的華為手機用戶，將無法更新Android作業系統，甚至不能使用Gmail及Google Play Store等多個手機應用程式和服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/google%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-173166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fgoogle%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C-173166&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ13Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=ab8a1228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/google%E5%B0%87%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%88%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-173166</a><br />\n<br />\n今次你仲唔仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以用AOSP Android嚟賣機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇得再update <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}